ADP Assignment 6

IDEA: (Tutor Service)

Sector: Education
Problem Domain

Students have a hard time asking questions or putting out ideas because they do not feel comfortable talking in front of a crowd or their peers hence resulting into possible failure for the student.
To solve the above stated issue, A software will be created that will pair students in CPUT based on their courses and other required details or where they can share notes, video call and voice chat.
The software basically allows student sign up using their student number and then add their courses, the app uses an algorithm to pair students together according to the similarities in subjects or courses taken to help them study and ease their work



